    medicinalUses: ["No accepted medicinal use. Muscimol is a potent GABA-A receptor agonist and ibotenic acid an NMDA glutamate-receptor agonist; both are used as research neuropharmacology tools (e.g. ibotenic-acid lesions in neuroscience), but the intact mushroom is not safe for therapeutic use.", "Some commercial 'Amanita muscaria' wellness products on the legal-gray market are derived from related species; A. pantherina contains higher muscimol concentrations and is correspondingly more dangerous."],
