  dnaBarcode: { itsClade: "Marasmius sect. Scotorchestes / 'oreades clade' within family Marasmiaceae (Agaricales); sister to other grassland Marasmius such as M. anomalus and M. collinus in multi-locus phylogenies (nrITS + nrLSU + rpb2)", keyPaper: "Wilson, A.W. & Desjardin, D.E. (2005). Phylogenetic relationships in the gymnopoid and marasmioid fungi (Basidiomycetes, euagarics clade). Mycologia 97(3): 667-679.", notes: "NCBI Taxonomy ID 181124; numerous nrITS reference sequences are available in GenBank and UNITE, and the species is well-resolved as a monophyletic terminal taxon, supporting the long-standing morphological concept." },
