    moisturePreference: "Moist but well-drained; not waterlogged; benefits from late-summer/early-fall rains penetrating the duff layer",
    indicatorPlants: ["Picea abies (Norway spruce, Europe)", "Picea engelmannii", "Abies lasiocarpa", "Vaccinium spp. (huckleberry)", "Hylocomium splendens (step moss)", "Pleurozium schreberi (red-stemmed feathermoss)"],
